related_questions.question: Who hires urban planners?
related_questions.snippet: The majority of planners work in government, and within that category, local government. Planners may also be employed at the state and federal levels. International organizations such a the United Nations and the World Bank also hire planners. Planners may also work with non-profit agencies or in the private sector.
